FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://warehouse.example.test

# Warehouse API

Valid integration fixture for inventory and shipment endpoints.

# Group Inventory

## Stock Items [/stock{?sku,warehouse}]

### List stock items [GET]
+ Parameters
    + sku: tea-001 (string, optional) - Filter by product SKU
    + warehouse: north (string, optional) - Filter by warehouse code

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[StockItem])

### Create a stock item [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (StockItemCreate)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StockItem)

## Stock Item [/stock/{stockId}]
+ Parameters
    + stockId: stock-123 (string, required) - Stock item identifier

### Get a stock item [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StockItem)

### Adjust stock quantity [PATCH]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (StockAdjustment)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StockItem)

# Group Shipments

## Shipments [/shipments]

### Schedule a shipment [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (ShipmentCreate)

+ Response 202 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Shipment)

# Data Structures

## StockItem (object)
+ id: stock-123 (string, required)
+ sku: tea-001 (string, required)
+ warehouse: north (string, required)
+ quantity: 42 (number, required)
+ reserved: 5 (number, optional)

## StockItemCreate (object)
+ sku: tea-001 (string, required)
+ warehouse: north (string, required)
+ quantity: 42 (number, required)

## StockAdjustment (object)
+ delta: -3 (number, required)
+ reason: order allocated (string, required)

## Shipment (object)
+ id: ship-456 (string, required)
+ status: scheduled (string, required)
+ carrier: groundline (string, optional)

## ShipmentCreate (object)
+ stockId: stock-123 (string, required)
+ destination: store-9 (string, required)
+ quantity: 3 (number, required)
